com.coveros.selenified.application

Interface Check

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    Assert, Verify, WaitFor

    public interface Check
    Assert will handle all verifications performed on the actual application itself. These checks are custom to the framework, and in addition to providing easy object oriented capabilities, they take screenshots with each verification to provide additional traceability, and assist in troubleshooting and debugging failing tests.
    Version:
    3.1.0
    Author:
    Max Saperstone
